OL,5, Sir James Dyson has lost his libel     
OL,6, claim against the publisher of the     
OL,7, Daily Mirror.                          
OL,9,FThe inventor was suing Mirror Group    
OL,10,FNewspapers (MGN) for libel over an     
OL,11,Farticle published in January 2022.     
OL,13,FMr Dyson told court the article was "a 
OL,14,Fpersonal attack on all that I have done
OL,15,Fand achieved in my lifetime and is     
OL,16,Fhighly distressing and hurtful".       
OL,18,FMr Justice Jay dismissed the claims.   
OL,19,FMGN said the judgement upheld "the     
OL,20,Fright of columnists" to share opinions.
